// on Mk.V.1 runs but we keep them as stubs in this ship — per budget
// pitfall the plan is: atom loader + synthesizer + smoke land now,
// observability gets wired per-atom in follow-up iters (design §5 plan).
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

// Check observability for a single atom. Returns (fired: bool, score: float).
// Packed as 2-float array because multi-float struct returns are buggy.
fn mkx_check_observability(atom_id: string, phi_vec: array, laws_state: string) -> array {
    // TODO(T10 subcoup): wire real MI(atom_flag, grad_W) — needs hook
